        <span class="tool-badge paid">Paid</span>
        <h3>AroraMSP M365 Audit Toolkit</h3>
        <p>PowerShell suite producing self-contained HTML reports for Microsoft 365 tenant security and Exchange Online mailbox storage.</p>
